Good Practices of Rest API:
---------------------------
My Rest Service should
  1. use Web standards.
  2. be friendly to the developer and be explorable via a browser address bar.
  3. be simple, intuitive and consistent to make adoption not only easy but Pleasant.
  4. provide enough flexibility to power majority of UI.
  5. be efficient and easily maintainable.
  
